headline: Capital One Financial Corporation to Webcast Conference Call on Second Quarter 2025 Earnings
summary: MCLEAN, Va., June 13, 2025--On Tuesday, July 22, 2025, at approximately 4:05 p.m. Eastern Time, Capital One Financial Corporation (NYSE: COF) will release its second quarter 2025 earnings results. Additionally, the company will host a conference call at 5:00 p.m. Eastern Time to review financial and operating performance for the quarter ending June 30, 2025.

headline: A $60 billion Visa, Mastercard slump seen as buying opportunity
summary: (Bloomberg) -- A report that large multinational merchants are exploring ways to bypass traditional credit-card fees presents investors with an opportunity to buy shares of Mastercard Inc. and Visa Inc., according to Wall Street analysts.
